data.description: This wonderful Craftsman style home built in 2020 offers a bright, open floorplan with nice finishes throughout. It is perfect for a growing family or if you have lots of relatives who like to visit. Situated on a half-acre lot on a cul-de-sac, it has a welcoming front porch. The main living area is open and airy with LVP flooring, crown molding, 9-ft ceilings, a spacious living room with gas log fireplace, gourmet kitchen with granite countertops, island, stainless steel appliances and dining area by glass doors opening to a back porch. A secluded main level primary bedroom has a tray ceiling, walk-in closet, carpet, and en-suite bath with double sink vanity, tile floor, granite countertop and step-in tiled shower. The main level also includes an office off the foyer, powder room, mudroom with built-in bench and laundry room. The upper level has a large, carpeted family room/loft area, bonus room, three bedrooms, two with a Jack and Jill bathroom, carpet, and another full bathroom with access from the third bedroom as well as the family room. A large fully fenced backyard has lots of room to play and great outdoor living areas including an open back porch and spacious patio with firepit. Located in  the beautiful Ravensbrook community close to Southern Pines and Whispering Pines, it will have sidewalks, a pool, pool house, open spaces, and walking trails connecting to Forest Creek and the Reservoir Park. It is just minutes from two shopping areas and is an easy commute to Ft. Liberty or the Triangle.
